INDIVIDUAL PRODUCT LICENSES
---------------------------
Each product within DevTrust will adopt its own license at the time of
public release, in line with the lane assigned in the master plan:

  Open-source products will be released under the Apache License 2.0
  unless otherwise noted in the product's own LICENSE file:

    - Repo X-ray            (Apache-2.0, planned)
    - CI Local              (Apache-2.0, planned)
    - Agent Trace SDK       (Apache-2.0, planned)
    - WhyChanged            (Apache-2.0, planned)

  Commercial products will ship under a proprietary license with terms
  to be defined per-product:

    - Smart Test Selector   (Proprietary, planned)
    - Agent-PR Reviewer     (Proprietary, planned)
    - Dep Upgrade Pilot     (Proprietary, planned)
    - TokenCost             (Proprietary, planned)
    - AgentGuard            (Proprietary, planned)

Until each product ships its own LICENSE file, all rights are reserved.
